{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":19173,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"你的公式貌似没法正常显示","timestamp":1592845452,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19181,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re : 诶这个怎么不支持行间公式...重打一下吧...\n$F_{辐射}=\\frac{\\mu_0 q^2}{6\\pi c}\\dot{a}$","timestamp":1592845513,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19185,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"$F_{辐射}=\\frac{\\mu_0 q^2}{6\\pi c}\\dot{a}$","timestamp":1592845524,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19190,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"$F_{radiation}=\\frac{\\mu_0 q^2}{6\\pi c}\\dot{a}$","timestamp":1592845554,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19191,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"$F_{\\text{辐射}}=\\frac{\\mu_0 q^2}{6\\pi c}\\dot{a}$","timestamp":1592845562,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19193,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"不能有中文","timestamp":1592845587,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19194,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Carol: 居然不支持汉字...","timestamp":1592845602,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19501,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"因为有这个辐射造成的力，它的加速度不会突变，所以无论是添加一个力还是撤去一个力，它的加速度都是逐渐增大（减小）到稳定值的。","timestamp":1592850637,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":19507,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"也就是说它在加速度减小的过程中仍然在受（辐射产生的）力，因此加速度自然不会直接就0了","timestamp":1592850832,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":20137,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"\\frac{\\mu_0 q^2}{6\\pi c}\\dot{a}","timestamp":1592876908,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":20470,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":3282,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这公式要求运动是周期性的，从能量守恒推导时有这个附加要求。这里的解都是非周期的，因此公式不能用在这里。","timestamp":1592879652,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":3,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":3282,"reply":11,"tag":null,"text":"根据辐射反作用力的亚伯拉罕-洛伦兹公式有\n$$F_{辐射}=\\frac{\\mu_0 q^2}{6\\pi c}\\dot{a}$$\n考虑一带电粒子在$0\u003ct\u003cT$时受恒外力作用，结合牛顿第二定律求解粒子的运动方程，会发现，$t\u003c0$时不存在加速度和$t\u003eT$时不存在加速度不能同时满足。\n求问应该如何理解这一结果？\n\n\n","timestamp":1592845414,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782584,"url":"","vote":{}}}